         <div type="traslation">
            <head>Translation</head>
            <p>Year called Bahudhānya, month of Māśi, dark fortnight, 12th day – the commentary of
               the <foreign xml:lang="san-Latn">Prabodhacandrodaya</foreign> is fully copied.
               Kāveripākkaṃ Muttaṇṇā copied with his own hand and the manuscript is complete. Honour
               to the illustrious the lotus-like feet of Muktiśvara together with Alaṃkāravalli.
               Honour the teacher Sāṃba.</p>
         </div>
